Help

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


  These are templates that are used in Wikipedia's "Wikipedia:" namespace.    The pages listed in this category are templates. 
 This page is part of Wikipedia's administration and not part of the encyclopedia. 
show
 Further template category notes 

 This category contains pages in the template namespace. It should not be used to categorize articles or pages in other namespaces.  To add a template to this category: 
If the template has a separate documentation page (usually called "Template:template name/doc"), add [[Category:Wikipedia namespace templates]]to the <includeonly> section at the bottom of that page. Otherwise, add <noinclude>[[Category:Wikipedia namespace templates]]</noinclude>to the end of the template code, making sure it starts on the same line as the code's last character.
